    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0001",
      "text": "Approval of an American National Standard requires review by ANSI that the",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        59.75,
        516.4,
        70.86
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0002",
      "text": "requirements for due process, consensus, and other criteria for approval have",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        72.29,
        516.43,
        83.4
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0003",
      "text": "been met by the standards developer.",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        84.77,
        324.04,
        95.88
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0004",
      "text": "Consensus is established when, in the judgement of the ANSI Board of Standards",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        105.29,
        516.36,
        116.4
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0005",
      "text": "Review, substantial agreement has been reached by directly and materially",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        117.77,
        516.33,
        128.88
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0006",
      "text": "affected interests. Substantial agreement means much more than a simple",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        130.24,
        516.44,
        141.36
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0007",
      "text": "majority, but not necessarily unanimity. Consensus requires that all views and",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        142.78,
        516.3,
        153.9
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0008",
      "text": "objections be considered, and that a concerted effort be made towards their",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        155.26,
        516.31,
        166.38
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0009",
      "text": "resolution.",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        167.74,
        202.38,
        178.86
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0010",
      "text": "The use of American National Standards is completely voluntary; their existence",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        188.26,
        516.26,
        199.38
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0011",
      "text": "does not in any respect preclude anyone, whether he has approved the standards",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        200.74,
        516.35,
        211.86
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0012",
      "text": "or not, from manufacturing, marketing, purchasing, or using products, processes,",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        213.28,
        516.32,
        224.4
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0013",
      "text": "or procedures not conforming to the standards. The American National Standards",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        225.76,
        516.19,
        236.88
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0014",
      "text": "Institute does not develop standards and will in no circumstances give an",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        238.24,
        516.3,
        249.36
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0015",
      "text": "interpretation of any American National Standard. Moreover, no person shall have",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        250.78,
        516.37,
        261.9
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0016",
      "text": "the right or authority to issue an interpretation of an American National Standard in",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        263.26,
        516.39,
        274.38
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0017",
      "text": "the name of the American National Standards Institute. Requests for",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        275.74,
        516.33,
        286.86
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0018",
      "text": "interpretations should be addressed to the secretariat or sponsor whose name",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        288.28,
        516.46,
        299.4
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0019",
      "text": "appears on the title page of this standard.",
      "bbox": [
        156.3,
        300.76,
        340.32,
        311.88
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 10,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
