      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0044",
      "text": "if any, patents may apply to this standard. As of the date of publication of this standard and",
      "bbox": [
        78.0,
        455.15,
        506.96,
        466.26
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p005_s0045",
      "text": "following calls for the identification of patents that may be required for the implementation of the",
      "bbox": [
        78.0,
        467.63,
        507.03,
        478.74
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
